page.title: 09HOUSING
page.content: In Parkneuk there are mostly council houses and the remaining few are private.Most of the council houses are flats and the others are terraced.On one side of the road there are mostly private houses.In Clunivar Street there are all flats.In the flats there are two houses upstairs and two downstairs.These flats are on one side of Blackburn Avenue.And from the end of them there are terraced villas. In Carnock about half of the houses are modern and private and the remaining half are quite old.The housing there has grown in the past twenty years.
